{"tid":2064754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：中美兩國人民友好不可阻擋","createTime":"2020-06-15T04:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-15T04:55:21.000Z","uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d0bd34be0e97e60db6143104a21efb82aacfac","tid":2064754,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情出現以來，中美兩國人民、企業、社會團體都在對方面臨困難時，第一時間伸出援手，在危難之際展現了寶貴的互助精神。這充分表明，中美交往具有深厚的社會基礎。中美兩國人民友好交往源遠流長，即便美國一些政客執意要為中美關系制造麻煩，也改變不了兩國人民友好交往的潮流。人民友好不可阻擋，逆潮流而動者終將為人民和歷史所棄。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://js.people.com.cn/BIG5/n2/2020/0614/c359574-34085652.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjs.people.com.cn%2FBIG5%2Fn2%2F2020%2F0614%2Fc359574-34085652.html&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8lDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=e9d91cb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://js.people.com.cn/BIG5/n2/2020/0614/c359574-34085652.html</a><br />\n<br />\n------<br />\n黃channel撐得好辛苦，可以幫手subscribe嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwlXPiafyjLc&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8lDHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=9d0be256\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wlXPiafyjLc</a>"},{"pid":"65a925cbf9d31d3ec5e8594d7e45e3e457dd3be1","tid":2064754,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:43:56.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"fa87db66b19dfcb02e8e9e24d87d32a13daddfd7","tid":2064754,"uid":91519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6693f4de21fd3d46ad8e820e3a77378e27ed59a","tid":2064754,"uid":26424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"人民友好唔係政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef309dff5ba8085ba034b254a2fe9abfcfbf244","tid":2064754,"uid":48040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0